      .section.section-additional-tips
        .container.sub-section
          %h2 Anything else before I dive in?

          %h3 Keybindings & HUD
          %p
            The default settings work but aren't the greatest. Below are a few settings I recommend. Note: you need to be in game to access these settings so start up an empty custom game.

        .container.sub-section
          .col-md-6
            %p
              %b Quick cast -
              It is faster to just hit the key to "Quick Cast" skills. As you are new to the game, having the range indicators is beneficial so make sure "Display Range Indicators when using Quick Cast" is checked off (at the bottom). This makes the range indicator visible when the key is pressed down. Upon releasing the key, the skill is fired.
          .col-md-5.col-md-offset-1
            .thumbnail
              %img{src: "images/quickcast.jpg", class: "img-responsive"}/
              .caption
                %P
                  while in game, esc > hotkeys > quick cast

        .container.sub-section
          .col-md-5
            .thumbnail
              %img{src: "images/minimap-scale.jpg", class: "img-responsive"}/
              .caption
                %p
                  while in game, esc > interface > minimap scale
          .col-md-6.col-md-offset-1
            %p
              %b Minimap scale -
              Make sure the minimap scale is set to 100. Bigger means easier to look at (and you want to get into the habit of regularly checking it).


